title: Starts of the Week + Week 17 Breakdown, Title Time - Fantasy Football Podcast for 12/30
description:
Week 17 is here and The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Week 17 matchup previews and Starts of the Week! Plus, injury updates, a new edition of “Never Not Working,” and the Boom Boom Kicker story continues! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for December 30th, 2021.
  
 (07:30) - Never Not Working
 (14:05) - NFL News
 (24:10) - Fantasy Forecast 
 (24:25) - Falcons at Bills
 (29:50) - Giants at Bears
 (33:20) - Chiefs at Bengals
 (39:20) - Dolphins at Titans
 (43:50) - Raiders at Colts
 (46:30) - Jaguars at Patriots
 (49:30) - Buccaneers at Jets
 (54:35) - Eagles at Washington
 (58:40) - Starts of the Week
 (01:11:10)  - Boom Boom Kicker of the Week
